Metals studs poke through the woodwork of this ornate chest. Judging by the fine craftsmanship, this strongbox appears to have been intended for public display.
A very old looking book, it has a slight foul odor coming from it. The pages are in a language that you don't understand.
A collection of summoning and domination spells revered by the Drow. It is believed by the Drow that the spells cast in the right order will unleash an unholy army of death upon the land.
This is a rather long and dry work on techniques and spells for summoning and binding creatures. The author is one Wedna Nemeln.
